  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Solo Holidays in Europe</h2>
<p>Feel a sense of freedom and independence like never before. Our single holidays are designed to help you experience the thrill of travelling solo, while still being able to meet like-minded people. With exciting excursions and activities designed to embrace the local culture and customs, you’ll get to see what makes each destination so unique.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13065806/tremezzo-lake-como.jpg" alt="Lake Como" data-udi="umb://media/39aacfbb6cc547809e1d47923c556765" /></p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Why book a singles holiday to Europe with Inghams?</h2>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">Inghams singles holidays are designed to give you the perfect mix of activities, exploring and relaxation. We provide a wide range of group excursions and walking tours which are all optional, so you can dip in and out of group activities as you please.</p>
<p>Our single holidays will take you to the most beautiful destinations in Europe. See, explore, and discover incredible cities, amazing landscapes, and stunning coastlines. You certainly won't be short of options when it comes to planning your next solo adventure.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>We're with you all the way</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089978/walkers-mountains-alps-314x193.jpg" alt="Self Guided Walking Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/890f49005ee74077a788bfe55aaa96cd" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Enjoy your holiday by yourself, knowing that you have Inghams excellent services and experience on-hand if you need it.</span></p>
<p>With friendly representative service in most of our resorts and a dedicated pre-departure team a phone call away, your holiday plans are safe with us.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Travel solo, your way </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13091814/switzerland-signpost-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b35fb28d5e294ba8910e960bda65c6f3" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Travel solo and explore Europe on your own terms. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whether you want a holiday full of activities and adventures, or simply want to relax by the shoreline of one of Europe’s beautiful lakes, our singles holidays offer the perfect balance of alone time and new discoveries.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>No single supplements </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13091813/women-by-lake-italy-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6982a5908467428ea76300bdb1eb0c48" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Many of our hotels offer a supplement-free option for travelling solo, or solo-specific rooms where you'll be able to enjoy your holiday just like everyone else. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You'll also have the option to join group activities, make friends and take advantage of many other benefits exclusive to solo travellers.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Solo Traveller Hotels</h2>
<p>Get away from it all, and have a holiday to remember. With our solo travellers in mind, we’ve selected some of the best hotels for people who like to travel alone. From Italy with its stunning lakeside views, to Austria and its majestic mountains, our single-friendly hotels are designed to make you feel at home, with plenty of things to do and see whilst you’re there. </p>
<div>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Discover our favourite hotels for one</h3>
</div>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4}" title="Hotel Europa SkyPool &amp; Panorama">Hotel Europa - 4 stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4}" title="Hotel Europa SkyPool &amp; Panorama"><img src="/media/13091011/hotel-europa-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5ae0655fe472415db3e35a20615d6498" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda, Italy</a></strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">Peace, quiet and a great view of the harbour are yours at Hotel Europa. It’s in the centre of Riva and has fantastic views of the lake and mountain vistas - perfect for relaxing.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/85e35c06cf8c49dfbf05b09243a3dab5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/85e35c06cf8c49dfbf05b09243a3dab5}" title="Hotel Medil">Hotel Medil - 4 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/85e35c06cf8c49dfbf05b09243a3dab5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/85e35c06cf8c49dfbf05b09243a3dab5}" title="Hotel Medil"><img src="/media/13091012/hotel-medil-dolomites-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/c27bb5dfb49843f8b4169bb20d172ed6" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites">Dolomites, Italy</a></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This classic Tyrolean style hotel offers beautiful, panoramic mountain views. The hotel’s spa which includes an indoor pool, sauna and Turkish bath are all included in the price. </span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/bfc3f71aa68e49c087bca906df5c9b7a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfc3f71aa68e49c087bca906df5c9b7a}" title="Bellavista Relax Hotel">Bellavista Relax Hotel, 4 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement </strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bfc3f71aa68e49c087bca906df5c9b7a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfc3f71aa68e49c087bca906df5c9b7a}" title="Bellavista Relax Hotel"><img src="/media/13091013/hotel-bellavista-relax-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/3ef09796b38b4577b56e586abf3e9ebe" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/6d3c5ed21e9544a292fe722aa587aa10" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d3c5ed21e9544a292fe722aa587aa10}" title="Lake Levico">Lake Levico, Italy</a></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Just ten minutes walk from the lake and surrounded by the Terentino Mountains, this hotel is in a beautiful location. You’ll have free use of the open-air whirlpool, heated outdoor pool, sauna and Turkish bath. </span></p>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/7eb0343d835d4ad48e3a18fd96cd2a0e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7eb0343d835d4ad48e3a18fd96cd2a0e}" title="Hotel Helga">Hotel Helga, 3 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement </strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7eb0343d835d4ad48e3a18fd96cd2a0e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7eb0343d835d4ad48e3a18fd96cd2a0e}" title="Hotel Helga"><img src="/media/13091014/hotel-helga-seefeld-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9cb81e2806684ba6b9a4a110b134192a" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld, Austria</a>,</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tradition meets modern comfort at this small, family-run hotel. Located in a quiet residential area, just 9 minutes walk from the centre, it’s the ideal starting point for a relaxing holiday in the Seefeld mountains.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/bccf2c2e72604aeabfe5cad69f032bcc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bccf2c2e72604aeabfe5cad69f032bcc}" title="Alpenhotel Fernau">Alpenhotel Fernau - 4 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement </strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bccf2c2e72604aeabfe5cad69f032bcc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bccf2c2e72604aeabfe5cad69f032bcc}" title="Alpenhotel Fernau"><img src="/media/13091015/hotel-fernau-neustift-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/e8a43a1d143f425e8b292895612afaca" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/f172dae360244d6b8c3d139aef4e83b5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f172dae360244d6b8c3d139aef4e83b5}" title="Neustift">Neustift, Austria</a></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This traditional hotel, with its beautiful countryside views and gardens, is just eight minutes walk from the centre of Neustift. You’ll receive a warm welcome from the Hofer family, who offer weekly guided walks of the Stubai Valley.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/c14c0cd55c494fb68059ed7c59a08bb4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c14c0cd55c494fb68059ed7c59a08bb4}" title="Hotel Haldenhof">Hotel Haldenfof, 4 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c14c0cd55c494fb68059ed7c59a08bb4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c14c0cd55c494fb68059ed7c59a08bb4}" title="Hotel Haldenhof"><img src="/media/13091016/hotel-haldenhof-lech-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/041fefb6df9246d79b5a9ace7ea4da65" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0}" title="Lech">Lech, Austria</a></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Just a short walk from the centre of Lech and run by the friendly </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Schwärzler family, you can expect a home from home atmosphere. They offer a variety of Austrian and international dishes for breakfast and dinner, to suit all taste buds.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;">
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e1fdabc5ec6e4e7ca010e2a7d37451fe" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e1fdabc5ec6e4e7ca010e2a7d37451fe}" title="Hotel Pointe Isabelle">Hotel Pointe Isabel - 3.5 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>Low single supplement and single rooms  </strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e1fdabc5ec6e4e7ca010e2a7d37451fe" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e1fdabc5ec6e4e7ca010e2a7d37451fe}" title="Hotel Pointe Isabelle"><img src="/media/13091017/hotel-pointe-isabel-chamonix-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b6dafbfacde647bf9b70c60cf7c6a560" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix, France</a></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Located in the heart of Chamonix, this hotel will appeal to those interested in exploring the local culture and activities, including walking. Soak up the mountain scenery and resort atmosphere from the terrace and bar.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13}" title="Hotel Schweizerhof">Hotel Schweizerhof, 4.5 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement  </strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13}" title="Hotel Schweizerhof"><img src="/media/13091018/hotel-schweizerhof-saas-fee-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a4a9c2c351574bff83e0f6108dde779a" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee, Switzerland</a></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Schweizerhof Hotel is located in the heart of Saas Fee, and is perfect for nature lovers and adventure seekers. Enjoy your stay with stunning mountain views in every direction and indulge</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> in the hotel's epicure restaurant or unwind at their spa.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/f6750f7ff4fb484f99ab3cb1b476b335" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6750f7ff4fb484f99ab3cb1b476b335}" title="Hotel Wilden Mann">Hotel Wilden Mann - 4 Stars</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>No single supplement </strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/f6750f7ff4fb484f99ab3cb1b476b335" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6750f7ff4fb484f99ab3cb1b476b335}" title="Hotel Wilden Mann"><img src="/media/13091019/hotel-wilden-mann-lucerne-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/bb65cc370a924ef487a3b77cdceda202" /></a></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne">Lucerne, Switzerland</a></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This enchanting hotel is located in the heart of Lucerne’s beautiful historic old town. Dating back to 1860,  the rooms have traditional charm and a boutique feel. If you appreciate a hotel with character, then you’ll love this cosy, historical gem.</span></p>
</div>
<div></div>
<div> </div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Book your singles holiday</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Book your independent solo holiday today! Solo holidays are a great way to just do what you want, when you want. Don’t miss the opportunity to explore your own interests and create memories that last a lifetime.</span></p>
<p><strong>Book online or call us on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</span> or book online.</strong></p>
